## PERSON NAMES — ALWAYS PROPER CASE

Friend and user names must read naturally in messages and UI — never leave them as the user typed them if the first letter was lowercase.

- **On save:** run `formatPersonName()` from `@/lib/names/format` before writing to `friends.name` or `users.name`.
- **In copy:** use `firstName()` from `@/lib/memories/categories` (it applies proper case). Do not hand-split names without formatting.
- **Examples:** `mary` → `Mary`, `MARY JANE` → `Mary Jane`

❌ "Hey mary, I left you a quick voice note —"
✓ "Hey Mary, I left you a quick voice note —"